00:13.926 --> 00:17.582
♪ Again and again and again

00:19.671 --> 00:22.587
♪ When darkness finds you
you'll be free ♪

00:22.631 --> 00:25.373
♪ Follow the lights and you
will see ♪

00:25.416 --> 00:29.290
♪ The instantaneous eternity

00:30.900 --> 00:34.730
♪ The instantaneous eternity ♪

00:36.775 --> 00:40.475
Life is a journey
and as we move along the path,

00:40.518 --> 00:43.956
we move closer to the light
that awaits us.

00:44.000 --> 00:47.525
But I say, "Why wait?
Why not launch yourself

00:47.569 --> 00:50.441
into that instantaneous
eternity right now?"

00:51.312 --> 00:54.967
It's, like, let's say you love
peppermint ice cream.

00:55.011 --> 00:57.231
And they say, "Well, you can
have peppermint ice cream,

00:57.274 --> 01:01.322
but only if you wait
like 75 or 80 years." Hm.

01:01.365 --> 01:03.411
But then you look
and there's that whole tub of,

01:03.454 --> 01:06.762
pile of peppermint ice cream,
the hog-and-dance stuff,

01:06.805 --> 01:10.113
the expensive stuff,
right there in the freezer.

01:10.157 --> 01:12.550
What are you gonna do?
You're just gonna look at it?

01:12.594 --> 01:15.727
No. You're gonna eat it, right?

01:15.771 --> 01:17.903
And that's what death is.

01:17.947 --> 01:21.559
It's eating that peppermint
ice cream on your terms.

01:24.910 --> 01:27.522
♪ Wash the sad out
no more pain ♪

01:27.565 --> 01:30.177
♪ All the dark
