01:41.101 --> 01:45.931
♪ The instantaneous eternity

01:45.975 --> 01:49.065
♪ Oh ooh ooh

01:49.109 --> 01:53.069
♪ Ooh-ooh ooh-ooh

01:53.113 --> 01:56.725
♪ Ooh ooh ooh ♪

01:56.768 --> 01:59.684
[telephone ringing]

02:06.213 --> 02:09.128
[instrumental music]

02:28.148 --> 02:29.279
[sighs]

02:35.329 --> 02:38.158
[grunting]

02:40.769 --> 02:42.640
[music continues]

02:44.555 --> 02:48.864
I say to you, ignore the
teachings of the sacred Storsh

02:48.907 --> 02:50.866
at your peril!

02:50.909 --> 02:53.260
My child, you need to be saved.

02:53.303 --> 02:56.611
The sacred Storsh
can give you bliss,

02:56.654 --> 02:58.265
joy and blessings to you...

02:58.308 --> 03:00.049
-Can you put s-some music on?
-Change your story.

03:00.092 --> 03:01.572
-I, I like...
-Change your story!

03:01.616 --> 03:02.965
I like whatever you like.

03:03.008 --> 03:05.620
You must change your story!

03:05.663 --> 03:08.579
[upbeat music on stereo]

03:14.585 --> 03:17.414
[instrumental music]

03:21.636 --> 03:25.335
-Hey!
-Oh, my God! Hi, smiley!

03:25.379 --> 03:27.119
-Hey, smiley.
-Hi! Mwah.

03:27.163 --> 03:28.643
Look, look. [chuckles]

03:28.686 --> 03:30.645
Look what I did. It's us.

03:30.688 --> 03:33.474
Oh, you made
your own toy surprise.

03:33.517 --> 03:35.040
Yeah, well,
there wasn't one in the box.

03:35.084 --> 03:37.521
Cute. Okay, that's great.
Well...

03:37.565 --> 03:38.914
Hey, how was your first day?

03:38.957 --> 03:40.394
Oh, it was, it was really good,
actually.

03:40.437 --> 03:42.047
Yeah, I think everything's gonna
be really fun,

03:42.091 --> 03:43.962
everyone seems nice
and, um, they...

03:44.006 --> 03:46.269
It seems like it's gonna be
really creative.

03:46.313 --> 03:48.402
