Claire.

03:50.142 --> 03:51.448
No, you can do it. Okay, okay.

03:51.492 --> 03:53.798
One, two, three.

03:53.842 --> 03:55.104
I don't know.

03:55.147 --> 03:57.193
-I-it's Rainbow Oats.
-[gasps] No way!

03:57.237 --> 03:59.282
-I love this bird!
-I know! I know!

03:59.326 --> 04:00.892
I actually said it's my
boyfriend's favorite cereal.

04:00.936 --> 04:03.025
That's so great! Rainbow Oats?

04:03.068 --> 04:05.157
I know, I know.
Well, how was your day?

04:05.201 --> 04:06.768
Oh, God, I had the best day.

04:06.811 --> 04:07.856
-Yeah?
-I had such a great day.

04:07.899 --> 04:09.379
Well, what, what did you do?

04:09.423 --> 04:13.035
Well, some very serious progress
on the job front.

04:13.078 --> 04:14.297
[gasps] You finished
your resume?

04:14.341 --> 04:16.473
-Ye... No.
-Ye...

04:16.517 --> 04:18.214
No, nothing like that.

04:18.257 --> 04:20.781
Um, no, but progress up here.

04:22.174 --> 04:24.176
Well, you know, it, um...

04:24.220 --> 04:25.700
It all starts with a thought.
[chuckles]

04:25.743 --> 04:26.701
Mm-hmm.

04:28.355 --> 04:29.834
Can I have a Rainbow Oat?

04:31.227 --> 04:32.446
Yeah.

04:44.327 --> 04:45.894
[Paul] Hey, should we do
that thing?

04:47.678 --> 04:49.985
-Yeah, let's do this.
-Yeah, yeah, yeah!

04:50.028 --> 04:51.334
-All right.
-[chuckles]

04:51.378 --> 04:53.510
-You ready? Okay.
-Yeah, okay.

04:53.554 --> 04:55.207
-Hm, that went well.
-Mm.

04:57.122 --> 04:58.733
-I'm gonna start.
-Do it.

04:58.776 --> 05:00.952
-Okay, ready?
-Uh-huh.

05:00.996 --> 05:02.867
♪ Do you like me? I suppose

05:02.911 --> 05:04.652
♪ Draw me like a French girl
Jack and Rose ♪

05:04.695 --> 05:06.567
♪ Sun goes up
and you milk that cow ♪

05:06.610 --> 05:08.395
♪ Slap that udder
on the big bad cow ♪

05:08.438 --> 05:10.048
♪ Watch that cow
drink all that grass ♪

05:10.092 --> 05:12.355
♪ Sometimes a donkey's
called an ass-k ♪

05:12.399 --> 05:14.052
♪ Me a question I'll tell you
what I'm thinking... ♪♪

05:14.096 --> 05:16.664
[Paul] Don't, uh... No, no,
every night, every night!

05:16.707 --> 05:19.710
-Aah, you were so close.
-Ah! Oh! At the donkey's ass.

05:19.754 --> 05:21.103
Yeah, the donkey
ask me a question

05:21.146 --> 05:22.670
and I'll tell you
what I'm thinking.

05:22.713 --> 05:23.888
[chuckles]

05:32.549 --> 05:35.944
-I know that smile.
-What smile?

05:35.987 --> 05:38.120
The smile,
less-than-a-smile smile.

05:38.163 --> 05:39.339
Hm.

05:40.818 --> 05:42.254
Can you tell me what's going on?

05:44.169 --> 05:45.519
-Come on.
-No.

05:45.562 --> 05:47.695
-Don't do that.
-No, it's fine.

05:47.738 --> 05:49.871
